<div type="letter">
<pb facs="1038985" n="279r"/>
<opener><lb/>Illustrissimo et Celeberrimo Viro
                        <lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-11887733X" type="person">Johanni Poleno</rs>
<lb/><abbr>S. D.</abbr>
<lb/><rs key="pers_DE-588-119166895" type="person">Nicolaus Bernoull<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice></rs>.</opener>
  <p><lb/>Post <del>felicem </del>meum in <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-2661604">Urbem Patriam</rs> appulsum, qui (Deo sit laus) feliciter
                        <lb/>contigit <date when="1717-07-03"><abbr>d.</abbr> 3. hujus mensis</date>, nil magis conveniens esse existimavi, quam T<subst><del>ibi</del><add>e</add></subst>
                        <lb/><del>ejusdem adventus meo </del><add>per epistolium</add> tam cito quam liceret salutare, <del>Tib</del> debitamque Tibi
                        <lb/><choice><orig><g ref="#agrav">à</g></orig><reg>a</reg></choice> me pro tot <subst><del>acceptis</del><add>mihi exhibitis</add></subst> beneficiis et sincerioris amiciti<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> testimoniis 
                        <lb/>gratiarum actionem renovare. Beabis autem me, si meum adver<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>sus Te animum talem<del> esse credas</del>, qualem ab ingenuo <del>et gra</del>ho<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>mine expectare debes, <add>esse credas</add> simulque nimi<choice><orig><g ref="#am">ā</g></orig><reg>am</reg></choice> m<add>ihi</add> libertat<del>i</del><add><choice><orig><g ref="#em">ē</g></orig><reg>em</reg></choice></add> ignosc<add>a</add>s si forte
    <lb/>ultra quam par est Te per rerum mearum curam molestiis onera<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>vi. In primis vero gratum mihi facies, si qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> ratione futuri nostri
                        <lb/>convictus si <add>qui</add>d<add>em</add> benevolentia
                        <lb/>tua molestias hinc forte <add>in <choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>dibus Tuis</add> enascituras superare velit:<!-- ToDo: Kontrollieren ob der Doppelpunkt hier korrekt ist. --> <add>a me Tibi pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>standa sunt, libere statues,</add><del>eaque ratione</del>
                        <lb/><del>porro</del><add>et porro</add> mecum, quamvis cum i<choice><orig><g ref="#mm">m̄</g></orig><reg>mm</reg></choice>erente, <add>ea ratione</add> ages qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> familiares decet.
                        <lb/>Prolixior ne sim tempus et negotia jubent; non autem finia<add>m</add><del>mihi</del>
    <lb/>antequam debitum honoris cultum <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr> <abbr>Dno</abbr> <rs type="person">Patri Tuo</rs><!-- ToDo: Verlinken, sobald Biblioeintrag vorhanden: Jacopo Poleni -->, Lectissim<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> 
    <lb/><rs type="person">Conjugi</rs><!-- ToDo: Verlinken, sobald Biblioeintrag vorhanden: Orsola Roberti --> et <rs type="person">liberis</rs> suavissimis<!-- Poleni hatte 6 Kinder: ToDo: verlinken, sobald Biblioeintrag vorhanden: Giacomo, Bernardo, Luca, Francesco, Eugenio, Elisabetta --> plurima ipsis dicta salute obtuleri<add>m</add> 
    <lb/>tam meo quam meorum <add>nomine</add>, imprimis <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-118509969">Patrui</rs> et <rs type="person">Fratris</rs><!-- Bruder von Nic. I B. --> qui <del>sal</del>Tu<subst><del>a</del><add>u</add></subst>m 
                        <lb/>in familiam nostram studium grata mente mecum agnoscunt.</p>
<lb/><closer><salute>Vale.</salute> <dateline>Dabam <rs key="place_GEO-2661604" type="place">Basile<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice></rs> <date when="1717-07-10">10. Juli<choice><orig><g ref="#j">j</g></orig><reg>i</reg></choice><choice><orig><g ref="#ndot">.</g></orig><reg></reg></choice> 1717.</date></dateline></closer>
  <postscript><p><abbr>P. S.</abbr> Oblitus eram Tibi <rs type="place" key="place_GEO-3171728">Patavii</rs> relinquere argumentum futura<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>rum mearum <rs type="keyword">Lectionum</rs>, id si placet hoc modo <choice><orig><g ref="#klammerauf">|:</g></orig><reg>(</reg></choice>nisi mutato pro<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>posito aliud <del>prius </del>interim nuntiem<choice><orig><g ref="#klammerzu">:|</g></orig><reg>)</reg></choice> scribi curabis: <hi rend="u">Explicabit</hi>
<pb facs="1038986" n="279v"/>
<lb/><hi rend="u"><rs type="keyword">Trigonometriam</rs> Planam et Sph<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>ricam, earumque utilitatem 
                          <lb/>pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>cipue in <rs type="keyword">Geographicis</rs> et <rs type="keyword">Gnomonicis</rs> ostendet.</hi><del> Obligabis</del>
<lb/><del>Obstr</del>Gratum quoque mihi erit, si qu<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice> exemtionis privilegium concer<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>nunt debito tempore pro me curare haud dedignaberis, ut et obsequia 
                        <lb/>mea denuntiare Fautoribus et Amicis meis, pr<choice><orig><g ref="#ae">æ</g></orig><reg>ae</reg></choice>primis <abbr>Ill.<hi rend="sup">mo</hi></abbr> <abbr>Dno</abbr> <rs key="pers_DE-588-104265264" type="person">Mor<pc type="hyphenation">-</pc><lb break="no"/>gagno</rs> et <abbr>D.</abbr> Comiti <rs type="person" key="pers_DE-588-1173256466">Alvarotto</rs>, cujus mandata <del>studios pro</del>ex voto 
                        <lb/>exequi conabor.</p></postscript>
</div>
